item.title: 【Requests】[REQ VID] - Taylor Swift - Speak Now World Tour Live (Deluxe / Target Edition)
item.description:
Hi,

I'd like to request for Speak Now World Tour - Live (Target Edition) if anyone has it. This edition was also released in Canada as the 'Deluxe Edition'. This special version of the DVD came with extra performances such as Taylor's cover of 'Nashville' and 'The Sweet Escape'. ISO format would be preferable.

I found a post here about this: Taylor Swift Speak Now World Tour Dvd Only Concert Target Edition | ShareMania.US. Unfortunately, upon downloading the eight-part RAR file, I discovered that this isn't the Target version as claimed by the poster. It was the original/standard DVD. It didn't contain the extra songs at all.

Thank you so much. I appreciate any help.
